title: Domestic Bond Issues for United States
notes:
This Series Covers Domestic Long-Term Corporate And Municipal Issues, Both For New Capital And Refunding; Data Can Be Continued Beyond 1938 (See Survey Of Current Business, February 1938). Source: Ilse Mintz, Determination In The Quality Of Foreign Bonds Issued In The United States 1920-1930, Table 13, P.88.

This NBER data series q10070 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 10 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter10.html.
